{"tid":2366068,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3少年於天水圍分涉襲警及管有物品意圖摧毁財產罪成 判監9-12星期不等","createTime":"2021-01-14T08:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T13:52:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8f318ad35dd6bf81bd9b8d6f0f9d2485e11a7dc6","tid":2366068,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12929&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVUxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=a70e2eb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12929</a><br />\n<br />\n#屯門裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#水佳麗裁判官<br />\n#1110天水圍 #判刑<br />\n#襲警 #攻擊性武器 <br />\n#管有物品意圖損壞財產罪<br />\n<br />\nD1:戚(17)<br />\nD2:張(18)<br />\nD3:張(19)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n<br />\nD1:<br />\n<br />\n(1)襲擊警務人員<br />\n被控於 2019 年 11 月 10 日，在天水圍嘉湖山莊景湖居近園林區，襲擊警員劉錦華<br />\n<br />\n(2)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器 <br />\n被控於2019年11月10日，在天水圍嘉湖山莊景湖居 11 座外，控制１枝伸縮警棍<br />\n<br />\nD2:管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產<br />\n<br />\n被控於2019年11月10日，在天水圍嘉湖山莊景湖居 11 座外，控制１枝15厘米長扳手及１個7厘米長衝釘器<br />\n<br />\nD3:管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產<br />\n<br />\n被控於同日同地，控制１把鎅刀、２對鉗子、５枝螺絲批、１把鋸鉗、１把電鑽、１個鑽頭、塑膠索帶、１把鐵造鎅刀、１枝鐵錘、４枝扳手、２套六角匙、噴霧膠布、１個四方匙、１枝火槍、２卷電線、２個電批、１個電動拋光機、９隻磨碟、１支罐裝石油氣、１套鑽嘴、１條螺絲、１枝膠水、１罐精密電器清洗劑<br />\n<br />\n速報:<br />\n<br />\nD1:3個月+6個星期監禁同期執行❗️❗️<br />\nD2:9星期監禁❗️❗️<br />\nD3:9星期監禁❗️❗️"},{"pid":"960836ad3ab79e990ed6a25982a4f854f89f5f4e","tid":2366068,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5469b2b9ff57a6112b45b9a1e669af9f559cb799","tid":2366068,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"低鳩能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301afb90665aa3d432e48a1615ca94fdb7f1bf7e","tid":2366068,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"死狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c34e8500e30a0954570c0507025fbf8fb8e190","tid":2366068,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:05:45.000Z","msg":"無做過？"},{"pid":"0b5e669b19f7466da10ecc7c35255d03ea3623c7","tid":2366068,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6746a71823fdbc52595d225def773ac7f4d3bd","tid":2366068,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4eaada58fa5dd766786c9792b3bb148cc9b717","tid":2366068,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:21:54.000Z","msg":"水佳麗俾上訴庭屌過幾獲之後釘到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"1131a7e4caa21e95c828adc7cb7ace89dc7ff538","tid":2366068,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"水佳麗變左咩都入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc09f1cf04c71a0c5c45828c993bee6b427eaca","tid":2366068,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"D3套野係咩解釋，咁都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99eddc269